{"tid":169351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"信報: 有建制選委指, 有中央人員前天南下, 容許選委按其喜好作出抉擇","createTime":"2017-03-24T06:53:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-24T07:41:10.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2bca0b060560801f0ce81f38e1a00e1236348ed2","tid":169351,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T06:53:47.000Z","msg":"容許自由投票 未必改寫結果<br />\n還有兩天便舉行特首選舉，雖然建制派一般都說大局已定，但昨天再有傳媒以頭版篇幅報道說，國家主席習核心在今次特首選舉中一直沒有「欽點」任何人，容許各人「自由選擇」，誰當選都接受。事實上，有建制選委也指出，臨近投票之時，有中央人員前天南下，其中傳遞的訊息是容許選委按其喜好作出抉擇，與傳聞不謀而合，亦令周日\t...<br />\n<br />\n（節錄）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www1.hkej.com/dailynews/commentary/article/1521751/%E5%AE%B9%E8%A8%B1%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8+%E6%9C%AA%E5%BF%85%E6%94%B9%E5%AF%AB%E7%B5%90%E6%9E%9C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww1.hkej.com%2Fdailynews%2Fcommentary%2Farticle%2F1521751%2F%25E5%25AE%25B9%25E8%25A8%25B1%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E6%258A%2595%25E7%25A5%25A8%2B%25E6%259C%25AA%25E5%25BF%2585%25E6%2594%25B9%25E5%25AF%25AB%25E7%25B5%2590%25E6%259E%259C&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVcf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=4ef1ffc6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www1.hkej.com/dailynews/commentary/article/1521751/%E5%AE%B9%E8%A8%B1%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8+%E6%9C%AA%E5%BF%85%E6%94%B9%E5%AF%AB%E7%B5%90%E6%9E%9C</a><br />\n<br />\n+X份野都講?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3a66b0861d1d2cce315dc9ed7b6d85ce6a14872","tid":169351,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T07:05:19.000Z","msg":"三個都係可以操控嘅候選人，邊個都無所謂<br />\n佢要嘅係puppet"},{"pid":"46fa408b29fbb50ec062413e440bdfdd7128d1e1","tid":169351,"uid":25556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T07:36:28.000Z","msg":"香港嘅選委奴才俾自由佢都唔肯自由"},{"pid":"b5b64ca642b3c7ba370a316fffe81f3fe5e53680","tid":169351,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201